jQuery UI Forms Plugin
By Fabian Topfstedt - http://www.topfstedt.de
Released under the MIT license

Description:
------------
A plugin that styles form controls in a jQuery UI compliant way.

Requires:
---------
jQuery and jQuery UI

Usage:
------
After adding the script sources of jQuery, jQuery UI and the plugin, you can
add the following snippet to add CSS classes to your forms and form elements.

$(document).ready(function(){
	$(document).uiforms();
});
